# CODEOWNERS for haveebot/brons-beach
#
# Mirrors PAL's agent-driven contributor autonomy pattern (locked 2026-05-04).
# Branch protection requires status checks (Vercel build) but no general
# approving review. Code owner review IS required on the paths below —
# sensitive surfaces still get operator eyes; cosmetic / brand / copy /
# component changes auto-merge once checks pass.
#
# Default (no codeowner): no review required — checks-only gate.

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Backend / API / data — operator review required
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/src/app/api/                   @haveebot
/src/middleware.ts              @haveebot
/src/app/admin/                 @haveebot

# Payment / messaging integrations
/src/lib/sendConfirmationEmail.ts  @haveebot

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Build / deps / config — operator review required
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/package.json                   @haveebot
/package-lock.json              @haveebot
/pnpm-lock.yaml                 @haveebot
/next.config.*                  @haveebot
/vercel.json                    @haveebot
/tsconfig.json                  @haveebot
/postcss.config.*               @haveebot

# Env (should already be gitignored — defense-in-depth)
/.env*                          @haveebot

# CI / Actions
/.github/workflows/             @haveebot
/.github/CODEOWNERS             @haveebot

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Free-merge surfaces (no codeowner = auto-merges on checks pass):
#   - src/app/*.tsx              Hero, LiveConditions, BookingForm, SiteNav, etc.
#   - src/app/globals.css        Color tokens + animations
#   - src/app/layout.tsx, page.tsx
#   - src/data/**                Products, venue, live-music content
#   - src/lib/openStatus.ts      Time/open-status util
#   - src/lib/sunCalc.ts         NOAA sun calc util
#   - public/**                  Static assets, photos, illustrations
#   - README.md                  Docs
#   - CONTRIBUTORS.md            Contributor list
#   - contributor-context/**     Contributor orientation docs
#   - Session Notes/**           Handoff briefs
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
